{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1285,"text":"I don't know if you've noticed,"},{"time":2379,"text":"but there's been a spate of books"},{"time":4051,"text":"that have come out lately"},{"time":5926,"text":"contemplating or speculating"},{"time":8068,"text":"on the cognition and emotional life of dogs."},{"time":12479,"text":"Do they think, do they feel and, if so, how?"},{"time":15350,"text":"So this afternoon, in my limited time,"},{"time":17290,"text":"I wanted to take the guesswork out of a lot of that"},{"time":19985,"text":"by introducing you to two dogs,"},{"time":22481,"text":"both of whom have taken the command \"speak\""},{"time":27305,"text":"quite literally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31266,"text":"The first dog is the first to go,"},{"time":34026,"text":"and he is contemplating an aspect"},{"time":38275,"text":"of his relationship to his owner,"},{"time":40431,"text":"and the title is \"A Dog on His Master.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":45431,"text":"\"As young as I look,"},{"time":47411,"text":"I am growing older faster than he."},{"time":50361,"text":"Seven to one is the ratio, they tend to say."},{"time":54386,"text":"Whatever the number, I will pass him one day"},{"time":57971,"text":"and take the lead,"},{"time":59839,"text":"the way I do on our walks in the woods,"},{"time":62760,"text":"and if this ever manages to cross his mind,"},{"time":66258,"text":"it would be the sweetest shadow"},{"time":68564,"text":"I have ever cast on snow or grass.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":73616,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76195,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79001,"text":"And our next dog"},{"time":82140,"text":"speaks in something called the revenant,"},{"time":85661,"text":"which means a spirit that comes back"},{"time":87692,"text":"to visit you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91458,"text":"\"I am the dog you put to sleep,"},{"time":95326,"text":"as you like to call the needle of oblivion,"},{"time":98778,"text":"come back to tell you this simple thing:"},{"time":101680,"text":"I never liked you.\""},{"time":103304,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":105914,"text":"\"When I licked your face,"},{"time":107808,"text":"I thought of biting off your nose."},{"time":110701,"text":"When I watched you toweling yourself dry,"},{"time":113680,"text":"I wanted to leap and unman you with a snap."},{"time":117788,"text":"I resented the way you moved,"},{"time":119970,"text":"your lack of animal grace,"},{"time":121856,"text":"the way you would sit in a chair to eat,"},{"time":124401,"text":"a napkin on your lap, a knife in your hand."},{"time":128703,"text":"I would have run away"},{"time":130161,"text":"but I was too weak,"},{"time":131911,"text":"a trick you taught me"},{"time":133547,"text":"while I was learning to sit and heel"},{"time":136612,"text":"and, greatest of insults,"},{"time":138745,"text":"shake hands without a hand."},{"time":142923,"text":"I admit the sight of the leash would excite me,"},{"time":146427,"text":"but only because it meant I was about to smell things"},{"time":149224,"text":"you had never touched."},{"time":154063,"text":"You do not want to believe this,"},{"time":155999,"text":"but I have no reason to lie:"},{"time":158365,"text":"I hated the car, hated the rubber toys,"},{"time":162449,"text":"disliked your friends, and worse, your relatives."},{"time":167235,"text":"The jingling of my tags drove me mad."},{"time":171183,"text":"You always scratched me in the wrong place.\""},{"time":174430,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":176432,"text":"\"All I ever wanted from you was food and water"},{"time":179210,"text":"in my bowls."},{"time":181402,"text":"While you slept, I watched you breathe"},{"time":183475,"text":"as the moon rose in the sky."},{"time":185805,"text":"It took all of my strength"},{"time":187422,"text":"not to raise my head and howl."},{"time":190478,"text":"Now, I am free of the collar,"},{"time":192978,"text":"free of the yellow raincoat,"},{"time":195488,"text":"monogrammed sweater,"},{"time":197366,"text":"the absurdity of your lawn,"},{"time":200396,"text":"and that is all you need to know about this place,"},{"time":203139,"text":"except what you already supposed"},{"time":206240,"text":"and are glad it did not happen sooner,"},{"time":208642,"text":"that everyone here can read and write,"},{"time":211883,"text":"the dogs in poetry,"},{"time":215233,"text":"the cats and all the others"},{"time":218240,"text":"in prose.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":220630,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222330,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}